FisyWiki Help
-------------

### Pages

* To create a new page, just create a new file in the **pages** folder.
* The initial page of each folder is **index**.
* Pages are organized according to the folder structure.
* You can, and should, use **markdown**.

### Layouts

* Layouts define the basic structure of a page.
* At the moment there are only 2 defined layouts.
  * default - the default layout.
  * 404 - the layout for non existing pages.
* Layouts are defined using markdown, html and widgets.

### Widgets

* Widgets can be used in pages or layouts.
* To place a widget, simply enclose it's name using double square brackets.
* You can pass parameters to the widget using |, # and =.
* Example: \[\[navigation|##separator=:##\]\]

| Name       | Variables                 | Default       |
|------------|---------------------------|---------------|
| Header     | theme                     | default       |
|            | title                     | FisyWiki      |
|            | subtitle                  | Page filename | 
| Footer     |                           |               |
| Content    |                           |               |
| Navigation | home                      | Home          |
|            | separator                 | >             |
